modelVersions.description:
While some "real" people were used in Canny and OpenPose ControlNets , intent and original "person" without a single source or direct likeness of an individual.

Generated using 3 full iterations.

  • Mixed prompts of various other embeddings and descriptors to create a roughly consistent "person". Trained 1,500 steps on initial set of data to create v1.1

  • Forked at best milestone, curated and mirrored training images, trained 3,250 steps to create v1.2

  • Forked again at best milestone, supplemented reference set with best results and trained 750 steps to get v1.3
